{"tid":2033311,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國總統國安顧問O’Brien： 國安法通過，香港唔會再成為亞洲金融中心","createTime":"2020-05-24T14:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T14:57:39.000Z","uid":128923,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"570fc429ec21f9d3324fad56ae5e21d62af9e9d4","tid":2033311,"uid":128923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:37:50.000Z","msg":"突發訪問<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I can&rsquo;t see how Hong Kong remains an Asian financial center,&rdquo; Robert O&rsquo;Brien tells <br />\n@margbrennan if Chinese national security law ending Hong Kong's dreams for Democracy is passed&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;That would be a tragedy for the people of Hong Kong,  but it would also be very bad for China&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/FaceTheNation/status/1264563827808534528\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFaceTheNation%2Fstatus%2F1264563827808534528&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=474d7214\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFaceTheNation%2Fstatus%2F1264563827808534528&h=f708c693\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/FaceTheNation/status/1264563827808534528</a>"},{"pid":"4984a7ebd439055dbbc1241a5184f2a95aa6e63f","tid":2033311,"uid":128923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:38:26.000Z","msg":"勞勃&middot;查爾斯&middot;奧布萊恩[1]（英語：Robert Charles O'Brien，1966年6月18日－）[2]，美國律師，現任美國國家安全顧問，美國人質事務總統特使<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/eb/Robert_C._O%27Brien.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fe%2Feb%2FRobert_C._O%2527Brien.jpg&h=592161df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1ba8900f456435c2922aeec7fd5017163174112","tid":2033311,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffebbfa1c4a2f6a452e6986479d1917e6e444905","tid":2033311,"uid":128923,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:39:23.000Z","msg":"白宮國安顧問：中國接管香港將招致美國制裁<br />\n<br />\n美國白宮國家安全顧問歐布萊恩(Robert O'Brien)在華府時間24日表示，中國即將審議制定針對香港的國家安全法，可能會招致美國的制裁，並威脅香港作為國際金融樞紐的地位。<br />\n<br />\n歐布萊恩24日接受美國國家廣播公司新聞網(NBC News)「會晤新聞界」(Meet the Press)訪問時說：「如此看來，隨著制定這項(港版)國家安全法，中國基本上將接管香港&hellip;<span style=\"color: red;\">若是他們這樣做的話，國務卿蓬佩奧(Mike Pompeo)很可能無法保證香港仍可維持高度自治，若是發生這樣情況，(美國)將會對香港和中國大陸實施制裁。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2065364\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2065364&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=a06692a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2065364</a>"},{"pid":"c33e59a126afc18f7a79e5c55bc3276a40f9fe3e","tid":2033311,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"570fc429ec21f9d3324fad56ae5e21d62af9e9d4","tid":2033311,"uid":128923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:37:50.000Z","msg":"突發訪問<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I can&rsquo;t see how Hong Kong remains an Asian financial center,&rdquo; Robert O&rsquo;Brien tells <br />\n@margbrennan if Chinese national security law ending Hong Kong's dreams for Democracy is passed&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;That would be a tragedy for the people of Hong Kong,  but it would also be very bad for China&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/FaceTheNation/status/1264563827808534528\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFaceTheNation%2Fstatus%2F1264563827808534528&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=474d7214\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%